casebody.data:
ELIZABETH GILDER v. UNITY GILDER and REUBEN GILDER, Administrators of John Gilder, and DAVID MARVEL, Administrator d. b. n. of Henry Gilder, (which said John and Henry were Executors of Reuben Gilder), and BATCHELDER CHANCE and ABSALOM GIBBS. Court of Chancery. Kent. Ridgely’s Notebook V, 371.

[July, 1827.]

[For this case, see 1 Del.Ch. 331.]
